{"id": 2991, "genre": 1004, "title": "你有多讨厌做家务？来测测你的家务人格", "description": "对我来说，每一件家务都是一场持久战。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Archive）", "record_count": 8723, "comment_count": 55, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190904211144SC35muehZPKoJzIU.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 6, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-09-06T17:00:00Z", "column": null, "normal_questions": [{"id": 5891, "content": "你的屋子一般是哪种状态：", "image": "img/question/question/20190904220604KmcCqDUbxhyFu48k.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 346103, "title": "乱到没处下脚", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 346104, "title": "乱，不过乱中有序", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 346105, "title": "时而整洁时而乱", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 346106, "title": "一直挺干净的", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 5892, "content": "一定要选一个的话，你最愿意【长期】承包的家务是：", "image": "img/question/question/20190904222850qHFJAgDyBPuC43Gp.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 346107, "title": "收纳", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 346108, "title": "扫地", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 346109, "title": "扔东西", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 346110, "title": "补充厕所卷纸", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 5893, "content": "以下哪个理由比较能让你有动力干家务：", "image": "img/question/question/20190904220700xOVRToG9l4vHYNmn.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 346111, "title": "有朋友来家里", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 346112, "title": "乱到自己看不下去", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 346113, "title": "今天刚好有心情", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 346114, "title": "爸妈/对象让我做", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 5894, "content": "做家务之前，你的第一项准备工作是：", "image": "img/question/question/20190906143511MsrVGoISEPHdQYxu.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 346115, "title": "合适的 bgm", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 346116, "title": "全套干家务的装备", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 346117, "title": "大块的闲暇时间", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 346118, "title": "晴朗的好天气", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 5895, "content": "开始做家务了，你的画风一般是：", "image": "img/question/question/201909042227157xC5zFmLb0nt9PEX.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 346119, "title": "说干就干", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 346120, "title": "能拖就拖", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 346121, "title": "就不怎么做家务", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 346122, "title": "先做心理建设再开始", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 5896, "content": "洗衣服时，你最常负责的环节是：", "image": "img/question/question/20190904222634NGXw3MnbY6C40dBs.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 346123, "title": "每个环节都自己来", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 346124, "title": "把衣服扔洗衣机/脏衣篮", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 346125, "title": "晾 or 收衣服", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 346126, "title": "叠衣服", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 5897, "content": "关于整理收纳这件事，你的风格是：", "image": "img/question/question/20190904222908efc1n2TGxad8RqvD.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 346128, "title": "只收拾身边的一圈", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 346129, "title": "要么不做要么 360° 无死角", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 346130, "title": "太麻烦了，不收", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 346131, "title": "随手清理，不留到第二天", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 5898, "content": "面对做饭洗碗，你的态度是：", "image": "img/question/question/20190904220535s7ZHqPSX9BzwQmNi.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 346132, "title": "尽量不做，外卖就行", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 346133, "title": "自己包圆，乐在其中", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 346134, "title": "只做饭不洗碗", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 346135, "title": "只洗碗不做饭", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 5899, "content": "对洗碗机、扫地机器人之类的新型家电，你的态度是：", "image": "img/question/question/20190904223138gZhe9T7kbX8O1mGS.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 346136, "title": "买了，而且经常用", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 346137, "title": "买了，然后在家吃灰", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 346138, "title": "观望，过了很久才下手", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 346139, "title": "比较怀疑，基本不买", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 5900, "content": "大扫除结束之后，你第一个冒出的念头一般是：", "image": "img/question/question/20190904223253Jr5gDoZTFjLPNidU.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 346140, "title": "累了，赶紧躺会", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 346141, "title": "挺有成就感，叉会儿腰", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 346143, "title": "憋屈，为啥人类要干这个", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 346144, "title": "还行，权当运动了", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}]}